      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "阎君知道，那还了得！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00031",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "行个方便吧！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00032",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "使不得！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00033",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "唵嘛呢叭咪吽……",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00034",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "哑唷哑唷……不要如此！众鬼卒，将刘氏清提，押上都城。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00035",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘清提上，上台子。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00036",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "一见母亲泪眼认，怎不叫人痛在心。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00037",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "长官，将我母亲焰火去了。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00038",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "众鬼卒，将刘氏清提，焰火去了。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00039",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘清提"
      ],
      "text": "刘清提站都城一言难尽，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00040",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘清提"
      ],
      "text": "罗卜我儿，儿呀！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00041",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄垛板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘清提"
      ],
      "text": "叫一声我的儿细听详情：",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00042",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘清提"
      ],
      "text": "儿本是阳世人相隔幽冥，今来到阴曹府把娘找寻。苦愁眉叫为娘心痛难忍，观不见儿容貌只听声音。想当初在阳间一家欢幸，儿每日在佛堂苦读经文。娘只说吃长斋何等侥幸，惊动了那铁树神开花见针。娘不该在佛堂咒骂神圣，娘不该用荤油添了佛灯；娘不该将白骨花园攘定，娘不该打僧骂道，骂道打僧，不听菩言，开了五荤，身受这灾星。我的儿呀！",
      "text_length": 156
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00043",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "缓锣鼓。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00044",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘清提"
      ],
      "text": "儿的父修正道西天成圣，哪知道为娘我受此苦情。娘只说阴曹府无有报应，有谁知为娘我到今日，蓬头盖脸，项带铁链，口内吞火，眼中点灯，何日里逃生？我的儿呀！",
      "text_length": 74
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00045",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "缓锣鼓。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00046",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘清提"
      ],
      "text": "求佛尊将为娘罪过改定，放为娘出都城是瞑目甘心。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00047",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘清提"
      ],
      "text": "儿吓，今当四月初八日，阎君赴龙华大会去了，你可哀告长官，将为娘放出都城，我母子也好相见。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00048",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "长官，将我母亲放出都城。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002018_e00049",
      "play_id": "01002018",
      "scene_id": "01002018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
